                                            "17",
                                            "M1701"
                                        ],
                                        "body": "In flood hazard areas as established in <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/alabama/irc-2015/chapter/3/building-planning#table_R301.2-1\">Table R301.2(1)</a>, <i><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/alabama/irc-2015/chapter/2/definitions#combustion_air_\">combustion air</a></i> openings shall be located at or above the elevation required in <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/alabama/irc-2015/chapter/3/building-planning#R322.2.1\">Section R322.2.1</a> or <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/alabama/irc-2015/chapter/3/building-planning#R322.3.2\">R322.3.2</a>.",
